# Tailwind v4 conventions

This project uses Tailwind v4 via `@tailwindcss/postcss`. Configuration is
CSS-first (no `tailwind.config.js`).

## Do

- Define design tokens with `@theme` in `app/globals.css`.
- Compose utilities directly in JSX; extract a component only when the same
  pattern repeats 3+ times.
- Use `@import "tailwindcss"` at the top of `globals.css`, not the legacy
  `@tailwind base/components/utilities` triplet.

## Don't

- Don't add `tailwind.config.js`; it is no longer needed and may be ignored.
- Don't use `@apply` in component files; keep it in `globals.css` if at all.
- Don't hard-code raw colors when a token exists.
